==Notable residents==
*Rachel Brouwer - Inventor
*Francene Cosman - First Mayor of Bedford, former MLA and cabinet minister, former President of the NS Status of Women
*Brendan Croskerry - Musician
*Nate Darling - NBA basketball player
*Vice Admiral Harry DeWolf - First commander of HMCS Haida (G63) during the Second World War and namesake to the Harry DeWolf-class of vessel for the RCN
*Ante Jazic - Soccer player for MLS team Chivas USA
*Shawn MacKenzie - Professional hockey player
*Brad Marchand - NHL Player for The Boston Bruins
*Anna Negulic - 2019 Pan American Games gold medal champion in the women&#x27;s 500 metres sprint kayak
*Geoff Regan - The 36th Speaker of the Canadian House of Commons
*Laura Regan - Actor
*Nancy Regan - Television host and self-employed
*Chase Tang - Actor and mental health advocate

